graph TD
    Client["Client / User"]
    
    subgraph KDC ["Key Distribution Center (KDC)"]
        AS["Authentication Service (AS)"]
        TGS["Ticket Granting Service (TGS)"]
    end
    
    TargetService["Hadoop Service (e.g., NameNode)"]

    Client -->|1. AS Request (Requires TGT)| AS
    AS -->|2. AS Response (TGT + Client-TGS Session Key)| Client
    Client -->|3. TGS Request (TGT + Authenticator + Service Name)| TGS
    TGS -->|4. TGS Response (Service Ticket + Client-Server Session Key)| Client
    Client -->|5. Service Request (Service Ticket + Client Authenticator)| TargetService
    TargetService -->|6. Establish Secure Session / Grant Access| Client
